item.title: @Tacticalbassin Matt Allen Breaks Down Lake Fork
item.description: Lake Fork Date Line: Early days video of Matt Allen of Tactical Bassin’ and his guide, putting the hammer to the big fish. Matt loses a giant in the trees, backs it up with a 12 lber then finishes off with a 7+ ! What a day on the lake for this guy!
